Title: Relates to including the mourning dove within the definition of "migratory game birds" and to allow for their taking
Summary: Allows for the taking of Zenaida macroura, commonly known as the mourning dove, as a migratory bird.
LawCode: Amd ยง11-0103, En Con L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the environmental conservation law, in relation to including the mourning dove within the definition of "migratory game birds" and to allow for their taking
